title: Ameriwood Expert Plum Work Center with Hutch
description:
Computer desk and hutch from contemporary Expert Plum office collection
Made of composite wood with rich brown wood-grain finish
Features include pull-out keyboard tray CPU cabinet letter-size file drawer adjustable open shelves and top rack for 45 CDs
Easy to assemble with household tools
Measures 58 inches wide by 24 inches deep by 59 inches high
